# MVS Media â€” Comprehensive Feature List

## 1. Authentication & Security
- **Secure Login & Signup**: JWT-based authentication for secure session management.
- **Google OAuth**: One-click login using Google Sign-In.
- **Password Management**: Forgot Password and Reset Password flows via email (Nodemailer).
- **Two-Factor Authentication (2FA)**: Enhanced security for user accounts.
- **Account Management**: Permanent account deletion.

## 2. User Profile & Settings
- **Customizable Profiles**: Bio, Profile Picture, Cover Photo.
- **Privacy Controls**: Public/Private account visibility settings.
- **Notification Settings**: Customize alert preferences.
- **Statistics**: View follower/following counts and profile views.

## 3. specific Social Networking Features
- **Follow System**: Follow/Unfollow users to build a network.
- **Follow Requests**: Accept or Decline follow requests (for private accounts).
- **Blocking**: Block and Unblock users to manage interactions.
- **User Search**: robust search for finding people.
- **Friend Recommendations**: (Implied by network logic).

## 4. Content & Feed
- **Dynamic Feed**: Personalized stream of posts from followed users.
- **Wellness Feed**: Specialized feed filtering for positive/mental-health-friendly content.
- **Infinite Scroll**: Seamless browsing experience.
- **Stories**: Share ephemeral photos/videos that disappear after 24 hours.

## 5. Post Management
- **Create Posts**: Support for text and rich media (images) uploads.
- **Interactions**: Like, Unlike, and Comment on posts.
- **Post Controls**: Edit, Delete, and Archive personal posts.
- **Saved Posts**: Bookmark posts to a private "Saved" collection.
- **AI Sentiment Analysis**: Automated positive/neutral/negative sentiment detection on posts.

## 6. Real-time Communication (Chat)
- **1-on-1 Chat**: Instant messaging with real-time updates (Socket.io).
- **Group Chat**: Create groups, rename groups, and add/remove members.
- **Typing Indicators**: Visual cues when users are typing (if implemented).
- **Notifications**: Real-time alerts for new messages, likes, and follows.

## 7. Privacy & Safety
- **Screenshot Detection**: Alerts when a profile screenshot is taken (Privacy Alert).
- **Content Moderation**: Blocking users and potential AI filtering.

## 8. Analytics & Insights
- **User Analytics**: Dashboard showing engagement metrics.
- **Content Insights**: Tracking performance of posts.

## 9. UI/UX
- **Modern Design**: Violet/Purple aesthetic with Glassmorphism elements.
- **Responsive Layout**: Sidebar navigation optimized for Web and Mobile.
- **Communities**: Interest-based groups (Beta).
